Interface WriteDao<T extends Dto>

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StreamWriteDao<T>

    public interface WriteDao<T extends Dto>
extends Dao<T>
    Data Access Object for creating, updating and deleting Data Transfer Objects

      • update

        default T update(T dto)
          throws de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.StorageException,
                 de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.ObjectWithIdNotFoundException
        Update one existing Dto in the data storage If the Dto is an instance of RepositoryItemDto, the updated Dto with a NEW EID will be returned.
        Parameters:
        dto - old dto
        Returns:
        the new dto, if the Dto is of type RepositoryItemDto its id will change!
        Throws:
        de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.StorageException - if the Dto can not be updated
        de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.ObjectWithIdNotFoundException - if a an item with the ID was not found

      • update

        T update(T dto,
         EID newId)
  throws de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.StorageException,
         de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.ObjectWithIdNotFoundException
        Update one existing Dto in data storage with a new ID If the new ID parameter is null, the ID is not changed -except for a Dto that is an instance of RepositoryItemDto, for which the updated Dto with a NEW EID is returned.
        Parameters:
        dto - old dto
        newId - non-existing new ID or null for no ID change/random ID (depends on type)
        Returns:
        the new dto
        Throws:
        de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.StorageException - if the Dto can not be updated
        de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.ObjectWithIdNotFoundException - if a an item with the ID was not found

      • updateAll

                           throws de.interactive_instruments.exceptions.StorageException,

        Update multiple Dtos in data storage If non-existing Dtos are an instance ofRepositoryItemDto, updated Dtos with a NEW EID will be returned.
